From: Siroshun09 <siro.shun8@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 2 Oct 2022 20:37:32 +0900
Subject: [PATCH] pufferfish Dynamic Activation of Brain

copy from Dynamic-Activation-of-Brain.patch:

This replaces the current method of ticking an inactive entity's
pathfinder 1/4 times with a new method that's dynamic based off how far
away it is from a player. If an entity is within 32 blocks, it gets
ticked every tick. If it's within 45 blocks, it gets ticked every other
tick. If it's within 55 blocks, it gets ticked once every three ticks.
(these numbers have since been changed, but the idea is the same.)

okocraft note:

- Remove 'dabEnabled' field in EntityType because it is not used
- Remove changes in VillagerPanicTrigger to keep the efficiency of golem traps

